b'Saint Seiya: Jashin Eris': b"Eris is the goddess of chaos and uses the body of Elien, who is a friend of Hyoga, to revive herself. But to be able to attack Eris, Seiya and his friends will first have to defeat the Ghost Knights. \n\n(Source: ANN)"
